 <br>
     1. Make friends. get a guild. find people you can get alone with, and do it early, find a guild before you make it to PvP lvls, you may not be able to get into an uber guild, but you'll have back up.<br>
<br>
     2. Learn your faction, if you have lousy guard faction you may be killed for defending yourself, and that just makes you madder. And you can't make any good money on trade skills selling to vendors without ally faction, amiable will get you a profit, but why not get the most out of your work.<br>
     <br>
     3. Never travel alone. unless your brave, foolish, or talented.<br>
<br>
     4. GET A RESERVE TUNIC, and anything else no drop. this is mainly a RZ rule, it's ac9 +3 dex, and is a dead sexy red banded look. it looks totally pimp on cats<br>
     <br>
     5. Never travel with money. if you meet someone with something to sell then meet them at a bank. it's the safe way for both parties and anyone that sais he's got his money on him is either brave, foolish, or trying to kill you<br>
<br>
     6. There is no rule 6.<br>
<br>
     7. don't cry when you get PK'ed. it makes you look weak. get revenge instead, it;s much more fun.<br>
<br>
     8. There is a rule 8, but at the last minute i decided it was to good, you'll have to buy my book.<br>
<br>
     9. the most important of all rules. know your classes. learn what each class can do, and what it takes to take them down<br>
<br>
     I can not promise that this well help you lead a succesfull life on the pvp, but it works for me. i hope it helps<br>
<br>
